why json:
-data representation format
-intergrates with most languages 
-has a simple sytanx  
-lightweight easy to read/write
-comonly used for APIs and config files 
Json types include :
-string 
-numbers {1,1.1 and scientific}
-boolen values 
-arrays []
-objects {"key" : "value"}  note -the values can be of any type mentioned above
json is valid javascript

